    (Nikita)

- Tidy:
  . Fixed bug #77027 (tidy::getOptDoc() not available on Windows). (cmb)

- Tokenizer:
  . Fixed bug #76991 (Incorrect tokenization of multiple invalid flexible
    heredoc strings). (Nikita)

- XML:
